# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# jkbmsr-releases (public CDN mirror) — environment template
#
# Copy to `.env` and fill in. `.env` is gitignored — never commit it; back it
# up somewhere safe. `.env.example` (this file) IS committed.
#
# This repo holds only public artifacts and needs no secrets to build. These
# are for manual `wrangler pages deploy` of cdn.jkbmsr.com (CI uses repo
# secrets). Firmware artifacts are normally published here by the
# jkbmsr-firmware release workflow, not by hand.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Cloudflare token to deploy the Pages project.
# Needs: Account > Cloudflare Pages:Edit.
# PROD HOME: GitHub Actions secret CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN on this repo.
# ROLL AT:   https://dash.cloudflare.com/profile/api-tokens
CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
